import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import { Icon } from '../../components/lock/Icon'
const address = '0xa62142888aba8370742be823c1782d17a0389da1'
const address2 = '0xc3672ef6721d1151699a8acd2072d529e73c6662'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"icon"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#icon"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Icon`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"primary-icon"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#primary-icon"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Primary Icon`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __code={`<Icon address="0xa62142888aba8370742be823c1782d17a0389da1" />`} __scope={{props,Icon}}>
    <Icon address='0xa62142888aba8370742be823c1782d17a0389da1' />
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"properties-table"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#properties-table"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Properties Table`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Icon} /></MDXTag>
